OL,3,CFarmers ask government to rethink
OL,4,Cgreen policy causing 'deep sense of
OL,5,Canguish'
OL,7,FThe have asked the Welsh minister for
OL,8,Frural affairs to re-think plans to
OL,9,Fmake farming greener.
OL,11,FThe NFU Cymru met with Lesley
OL,12,FGriffiths MS to discuss the
OL,13,Fsustainable farming scheme.
OL,15,FThe Union says they've given her a
OL,16,Flist of policy recommendations to
OL,17,Faddress the concerns and worries of
OL,18,Fthousands of farmers who have attended
OL,19,FNFU Cymru roadshows and events over
OL,20,Fthe past month.
