OL,5,Canguish'
OL,7,FNFU Cymru President, Aled Jones says
OL,8,Fthere is a "deep sense of anguish
OL,9,Fwithin the industry" over the plans.
OL,11,FThe is the 's plan to replace EU
OL,12,Ffarming subsidies, which Welsh farmers
OL,13,Fcan no longer access after Brexit.
OL,15,FIt would mean farmers have to plant
OL,16,F10% of their land with trees, and a
OL,17,Ffurther 10% would become habitat for
OL,18,Fwildlife in order to get government
OL,19,Fpayments to support their farms.
