OL,7,FThis is, in part, to help the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment meet their own target of
OL,9,Fplanting 43,000 hectares of woodland
OL,10,Fby 2030.
OL,12,FBut farmers say the policy isn't fair,
OL,13,Fand have been protesting against them,
OL,14,Fincluding sending convoys of tractors
OL,15,Fto block Welsh roads.
OL,17,FThe controversy attention of TV
OL,18,Fpresenter Jeremy Clarkson , a farmer
OL,19,Fhimself, who called the policy
OL,20,F"completely daft."
