OL,7,FThe Top-Gear star began working his
OL,8,Fown fields at Diddly-Squat Farm in the
OL,9,Fwest country in 2021, documenting his
OL,10,Fjourney in the TV show Clarkson's Farm.
OL,12,FThe union has raised concerns that the
OL,13,Ftarget, if implemented, could force
OL,14,Ffarmers to give up land they use to
OL,15,Fgrow crops in order to plant trees,
OL,16,Fmeaning less food production.
OL,18,FA commissioned by the Welsh government
OL,19,Fon the consultation of the scheme says
OL,20,Fit could mean 5,500 job losses.
