OL,7,FThe Minister for Rural Affairs Lesley
OL,8,FGriffiths said: "I meet with the
OL,9,Ffarming unions regularly and I wanted
OL,10,Fto have a meeting as soon as possible
OL,11,Fafter our Sustainable Farming Scheme
OL,12,Froadshows and theirs had been
OL,13,Fcompleted.
OL,15,F"I'd like to thank them for joining me
OL,16,Ftoday, it was good to hear the
OL,17,Ffeedback they had from their events.
OL,18,FWe will consider this in addition to
OL,19,Fthe feedback we've noted from our
OL,20,Fevents.
