OL,7,F"Many of the issues discussed were
OL,8,Fcommon with those we heard from the
OL,9,F3,200 farmers who've attended the
OL,10,FWelsh Government events.
OL,12,F"I reiterated to them this is a
OL,13,Fgenuine consultation. It is still
OL,14,Fopen, and I would continue to urge
OL,15,Fpeople to take part and give us their
OL,16,Fviews. We will consider every
OL,17,Findividual response.
