OL,7,F"Once the consultation is over I will
OL,8,Freceive a detailed analysis of the
OL,9,Fresponses, and as I've said before I
OL,10,Fwould expect to make changes to the
OL,11,Fscheme as a result.
OL,13,F"It is vitally important people take
OL,14,Fpart in the consultation. Please do
OL,15,Ffind time to respond as your views
OL,16,Fmatter."
